01:57:04.128 --> 01:57:09.698
Guido: Seven married ladies from
the hosting countries.

01:57:10.397 --> 01:57:13.012
Sette donne.

01:57:14.395 --> 01:57:17.287
Hosting, hosting countries.

01:57:18.256 --> 01:57:24.768
Who have never been before to the Lotus
Feet of Shri Mataji.

01:57:25.872 --> 01:57:33.480
Qualche donna italiana che non sia mai
stata prima ai Piedi di Shri Mataji.

