03:05:01.775 --> 03:05:07.499
Guido: As you all know, Shri Mataji has
been always trying to encourage art,

03:05:07.700 --> 03:05:11.792
to support the artists, and She is
travelling all over the world

03:05:11.993 --> 03:05:19.369
collecting pieces, trying to improve
the artisans

03:05:19.570 --> 03:05:22.358
and handicraft all over the world.

03:05:22.559 --> 03:05:30.223
So this time Italy has found some art
pieces from different artists,

03:05:30.424 --> 03:05:36.580
in Sardinia, and we would like
to present Shri Mataji.

03:05:36.875 --> 03:05:46.652
They are all different way of treating
the ceramics.

03:05:51.237 --> 03:05:54.417
Shri Mataji: Where did you get this?
Guido: Sardinia, Shri Mataji.

03:05:54.618 --> 03:05:57.023
Shri Mataji: Eh? Guido: Sardinia.
Shri Mataji: What’s this? Yogini: Sardinia.

03:05:57.224 --> 03:06:01.040
Guido: This is cooked in a wood oven.
Shri Mataji: Eh?

03:06:01.249 --> 03:06:06.097
Guido: Wood oven. Shri Mataji: Wood?
Guido: Wood oven. In the oven...

03:06:06.298 --> 03:06:10.779
Shri Mataji: It’s a marble? (Unclear)
Guido: No, it's made in a wood oven.

03:06:10.987 --> 03:06:15.404
Shri Mataji: Ah! And where did you find it?
Guido: In Sardinia.

03:06:15.605 --> 03:06:23.667
Shri Mataji: Sardinia!
This is Sardinian. That’s beautiful.

03:06:50.064 --> 03:06:54.938
Guido: The another one (?) is from Sicily.
This is all Sardinian.

03:06:55.146 --> 03:06:58.123
Shri Mataji: All Sardinians?
Guido: All Sardinians.

03:07:13.732 --> 03:07:18.153
Shri Mataji: All such is a... (unclear)
Guido: No, only that one.

03:08:36.938 --> 03:08:46.757
Now, you see, every puja I give presents
to all the countries who are hosting:

03:08:46.965 --> 03:08:50.475
to all the ladies, all the men,
the leaders.

03:08:50.676 --> 03:08:56.900
Only in Guru puja, I’m sorry, I’m not
supposed to give any presents to anyone.

03:08:57.109 --> 03:09:05.394
It’s a thing when the guru, only, has
to grab everything from you!

03:09:14.577 --> 03:09:17.364
All this has to be given only on Guru puja:

03:09:17.565 --> 03:09:21.001
specially the saris, that have been given
to Me,

03:09:21.211 --> 03:09:24.650
are all to be given only during Guru puja.

03:09:24.851 --> 03:09:33.794
But I’m sorry, I can’t give anything
to the leaders or to anyone on this day.

03:09:33.995 --> 03:09:37.353
I hope you people don’t mind.

03:09:49.917 --> 03:09:53.845
To be the guru and to be Mother is a very
difficult thing

03:09:54.046 --> 03:10:02.718
because, if you see, the gurus have been
very strict disciplinarians:

03:10:02.919 --> 03:10:08.458
they always try to discipline the disciples
and [be] quite hard with them.

03:10:08.659 --> 03:10:13.859
But the mother can’t be that hard, you see.
This is the trouble with the motherhood is!

03:10:14.060 --> 03:10:20.278
That may be one of the reasons that people
take, sometimes, Sahaja Yoga for granted.

03:10:20.479 --> 03:10:26.202
But you should not, because you have got
your realisation now.

03:10:26.403 --> 03:10:29.898
Now you are realised-souls, you are
masters,

03:10:30.099 --> 03:10:32.475
so you should look after your ascent.

03:10:32.676 --> 03:10:35.755
I don’t have to tell you what [is] to be
done,

03:10:35.956 --> 03:10:40.713
because you have the light in your hand
and you can do that very well.

03:10:40.914 --> 03:10:46.527
I hope today’s lecture, you liked very much
and you don’t mind

03:10:46.728 --> 03:10:51.775
if I have said something that might have
upset you a little bit.

03:10:51.976 --> 03:10:57.360
But it is a thing [that] one has to see
because we all have to grow

03:10:57.561 --> 03:11:02.634
inside and outside and we have to spread
Sahaja Yoga everywhere.

03:11:02.835 --> 03:11:06.988
So we should see everyone - whether
it’s a woman or a man -

03:11:07.189 --> 03:11:11.175
we should see how many people we have
given realisation to.

03:11:11.376 --> 03:11:15.844
It’s very important that you should start
giving realisation all over the world.

03:11:16.045 --> 03:11:21.527
In this fashion it will spread and I don’t
have to then travel so much

03:11:21.728 --> 03:11:24.839
as nowadays I am travelling still.

03:11:25.040 --> 03:11:29.836
I think, you all should take it up upon
yourself that you will do,

03:11:30.043 --> 03:11:35.624
at least if not travelling, around your
cities, around in your places of work,

03:11:35.825 --> 03:11:39.844
you can start talking about Sahaja Yoga
openly.

03:11:40.045 --> 03:11:44.504
All the blessings are there, all the powers
are there, you can work it out very well.

03:11:44.705 --> 03:11:48.207
Anybody you find difficult you give bandhan
and can manage things.

03:11:48.408 --> 03:11:51.305
You know it very well. You know everything
about Sahaja Yoga,

03:11:51.506 --> 03:11:54.769
so I don’t have to tell you about it.
Only thing: use it!

03:11:54.970 --> 03:11:58.931
Even if you have all the instruments and
if you don’t use it, it won’t work out.

03:11:59.132 --> 03:12:04.744
With all My love, with all My blessings,

03:12:04.945 --> 03:12:07.686
I say goodbye now to you, for the time
being.

03:12:07.887 --> 03:12:10.681
Thank you.

